# 3. Scenario Purpose

{{ description }}

This scenario establishes Level-5 enterprise continuity by coordinating executive visibility, governance-aware escalation, cross-domain survivability, continuity validation, and enterprise evidence generation.

---

# 4. Operational Relevance

Continuity scenarios validate whether enterprise services can remain governable, visible, and coordinated during large-scale operational disruption.

This scenario focuses on organizational survivability, executive escalation visibility, cross-domain coordination, and continuity governance.

---

# 5. Design Reasoning

This scenario intentionally remains within the Level-5 Continuity lifecycle boundary.

The design allows enterprise continuity coordination, executive escalation visibility, governance-aware validation, and organizational survivability workflows.

The scenario prioritizes enterprise continuity coordination over infrastructure-only failover execution.

