# 10. Implementation Approach

The implementation approach follows an enterprise continuity coordination flow.

Enterprise degradation visibility activates continuity coordination workflows. Executive escalation, cross-domain survivability coordination, governance validation, and continuity evidence aggregation are coordinated through enterprise operational processes.

